if we want a button with so much text and line breaks we have to create an xml and create a new data connection - retrieve from xml 
(when getting the xml choose Resource and add the xml as resource)

Note: in design the text is not visible ...

http://www.bizsupportonline.net/blog/2010/display-button-text-label-infopath-two-lines.htm

to update the xml click on Data - Resources y Add , when asked click on replace and the data will be refreshed...

